title: Cowboy Bebop Manga
description:
Cowboy Bebop (?????????, Kaub?i Bibappu?) is a Japanese anime series directed by Shinichiro Watanabe and written by Keiko Nobumoto, it consists of 26 episodes (called "sessions"). It is produced by Sunrise. It follows the adventures of a group of bounty hunters traveling on their spaceship, the Bebop, in the year 2071.


Manga based off of the Anime.  Enjoy!!!

As usual, thanks to the original scanners.
